Give Antigravity the ADK skills
For Antigravity to build ADK agents well, it needs the ADK skill set. These are bundled references for the ADK API, project scaffolding, the agents-cli workflow, and evaluation. Installing the agents-cli toolchain also installs these skills into your coding agent. 
